author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the state of Windows 11, I normally wouldn't do this but it seems each week this month something random breaks in Windows and yesterday they somehow managed to break the Task Manager's basic function on terminating itself. How does this happen? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!

title: Microsoft Broke The Windows Task Manager...
